frus:attachment.p:
The officer in command of the unit will then send: 
                            1.

The report of the D.A.G. 3d echelon;
                            2.

The soldier’s certificate of birth;
                            3.

The certificate obtained by the soldier as to the publication of
                                the banns;
                            4.

The soldier’s statutory declaration;
                            5.

A translation of the several documents above named certified to be
                                true by an interpreter officer;
